  "detailed_description": "A casual game in which you have to break boards for a cute karate cat. In order not to lose, the player needs to follow the cat’s concentration indicator and not accidentally hit a brick. When a player picks up a combo, the cat becomes furious and a brick is not a problem for him.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152410/extras/99eed3ba9b75aeb878f3f64cef7a6618.webp?t=1593102733\" width=616 height=43 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152410/extras/964e6c9cb928cd4c46a3a61dd943bc73.webp?t=1593102733\" width=616 height=6 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152410/extras/d0b9a2d2dfb5fa1c0938f45ac20342e5.poster.avif?t=1593102733\" width=600 height=137 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152410/extras/d0b9a2d2dfb5fa1c0938f45ac20342e5.webm?t=1593102733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152410/extras/964e6c9cb928cd4c46a3a61dd943bc73.webp?t=1593102733\" width=616 height=6 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152410/extras/dcb16bbc30291ce31ee7215a55b9864b.apng?t=1593102733\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152410/extras/dcb16bbc30291ce31ee7215a55b9864b.poster.avif?t=1593102733\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=142 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/